    GCVisualization.register_event_hook with visualizer as visualizer and event as "error_handler" and handler as error_handler
    
    Let result1 be assert_not_none with value as visualizer.event_hooks["error_handler"] and message as "Error handler should be registered"
    
    Note: Test error handling during visualization
    GCVisualization.handle_visualization_error with error as "test_error" and visualizer as visualizer
    
    Let result2 be assert_greater_than with actual as visualizer.state.error_count and expected as 0 and message as "Error count should be incremented"
    
    Return result1 and result2

